n!
n! = \int_0^\infty t^n e^{-t} \: dt
n!
{a_n}{a_{n-1}} \cdots {a_0}
\sum_{i=0}^{n} a_i 10^i 
a_0 + 10 \left( a_1 + 10 \left( \cdots + 10 a_n \right) \cdots \right)
a_0 + 2 \left( a_1 + 3 \left( \cdots + (n+1) a_n \right) \cdots \right)
0 \le a_0 \le 1, 0 \le a_1 \le 2, \ldots, 0 \le a_n \le n
n! = 10 \cdots 0
